  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "British Prime Minister Johnson resigns",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "British Prime Minister Boris Johnson, who continued to say that he would not be influenced by anyone, resigned from the leadership of the Conservative Party and the position of Prime Minister.",
        "The Prime Minister was under pressure from his cabinet members as well as the Attorney General to resign.",
        "Johnson has been accused of violating health laws during the lockdown and giving a top government post to party member Chris Pincher, who was accused of sexually harassing women. That is why he was pressured to resign."
      ],
